ID=415.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> I wanna kill the king.  Currently ally, but wanna get RoS faction up without spending a month inside MM.  How would I go about killing this guy without having to kill EVERY SINGLE GUARD?  I don't mind killing the guards, but hate to if it's not necessary since they're not gonna help RoS faction.<br>
<br>
Is there an area that the king can be pulled to for easy dispatch?  Would it be possible to simply pull him outside of the throne room without aggroing the guards, cept for roamers?  Using lvl 60 pullers of course. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umodauth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>modauth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 113<br> <font color=#333333>(9/12/02 12:16:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> You can get non kos to Ring of Scale in one run to Mistmoore. Grab some friends and fight your way in to nice big open room. AE everything. Mem all your best aoe's and scintillaton and go to town. If your willing to take one death you can do it without a cleric even. We did it when going there for a pali's epic piece a while back. I went from scowls to indifferent with RoS. Only took a couple hours of aoe. <br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubandose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bandose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 107<br> <font color=#333333>(9/12/02 7:57:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> We did pretty fast pulls one night with a 60 bard pulling with aggro song and me AEing.  This went on for nearly 2 hours and I'm still threatening to RoS.  I want dorf blood! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urazha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Razha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#333333>(9/18/02 4:52:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> Dorf king in Kaladim is a MASSIVE faction hit.  You can be non-kos to ros after just a few hours of killing him comming from max kos.  There is no reason to waste your time in MM, which contrary to the previous poster, will take you a long time to do. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubandose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bandose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 122<br> <font color=#333333>(10/1/02 12:31:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> I still have the same problem with Keledim...I can't figure out how to single pull the king or where to pull him to avoid killing every guard.<br>
<br>
As for faction hits in keledim, farming orcs for a short while will fix most of that and then belts and shoulder pads will probably fix the rest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujoydiv6996.showPublicProfile?language=EN>joydiv6996</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(10/1/02 6:20:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Kaladim problem</span><hr size=1> Well I have ally status with the ring of scale for me it was getting minions of scale faction I could never seem to find.  I got my RoS faction from hunting assorted bards throughout  Norrath like Travis, Vhalen, etc... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showPrevMessage?topicID=415.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showNextMessage?topicID=415.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.threadControl?topicID=415.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=415.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive 